snippet.textDisplay: I'm not a south Asian & I did not hear the original song. The first time I heard this I thought it was a masterpiece. From a pure musical perspective this is a really good song. I don't know why everyone's complaining about it. Maybe you're too biased to the original that you fail to notice this version's brilliance. it takes someone who's totally strange to your musical history to recognize the sheer magic of this song. So try to enjoy it and don't spoil it for others please.
